次個肥婆仲唔俾人屌撚死?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"冇用, 德國人普遍仲係算支持佢,雖然冇前幾年咁高<br />\n<br />\n西歐真係特別係離地撚,完全唔知中国有咩威脅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"所以要多啲人打國際戰線"},{"pid":"19800531ba58cd56b1f62d5d9e19fbfcf31872ad","tid":1832191,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03d49cf8323ff440cc81cde63974dfc19d84af6","tid":1832191,"uid":80560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"東德妖婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年ww2完成咗應該行Roosevelt Plan<br />\n任何一個統一的德國都是邪惡軸心的助攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"仲有本民前手足被德國收留<br />\n<br />\n德國頂多係左膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}